- "The fact is that..."
- "Well, I think we have [entered / entered a situation where]..." (frames thesis; not hedged refinement)
- "Now, what exactly do I mean by that? I think as a result of the fact that X—and that Y will almost certainly Z—you axiomatically have..."
- "The structural picture is..."
- "The realist observation here would be direct..."

